 USA!\\\".\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6495006209661381, \"rank\": 0.5361448378409711, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6495006209661381, \"rank\": 0.5361448378409711, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2667, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6495006209661381, \"rank\": 0.5361448378409711, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"her uneven bars\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"ease\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"the delight\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15,000 fans\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"chants\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was awarded 14.400.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The star-studded crowd that included tennis great Serena Williams and the most successful Olympian ever, swimmer Michael Phelps, also roared their approval when Biles' teammates Sunisa Lee and Jordan Chiles c